{"id":1237,"date":"2024-08-04T00:19:32","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T00:19:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1237"},"modified":"2024-08-04T00:19:32","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T00:19:32","slug":"mission-040","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-040\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #040: More than a Game"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #040: More Than a Game<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Battle Frontier &#8211; Ace Trainer in the gate from Seaport City<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Become Pok\u00e9mon Champion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Win 100 Frontier Battles<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>200 BP<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>If you\u2019ve become Pok\u00e9mon Champion, the Battle Frontier becomes open to you. An Ace Trainer in the gate area challenges you to win 100 Frontier Battles. If you do so, you\u2019ll get 200 BP.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>After you become Pok\u00e9mon Champion, the Battle Frontier will be available to you. It\u2019s reached through a gate between the Pok\u00e9mon Center and the Poke Mart in Seaport City.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/040\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-battle-frontier-gate-in-seaport-city.jpg\" alt=\"The Battle Frontier gate in Seaport City \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Battle Frontier gate in Seaport City<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you enter the gate for the first time, you\u2019ll be given a Frontier Card.<\/p>\n<p>The currency inside the Battle Frontier is Battle Points, and the Frontier Card enables you to track them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/040\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-mission-at-hand.jpg\" alt=\"The mission at hand \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mission at hand<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Right before you enter the Battle Frontier proper, speak to the Ace Trainer. She\u2019ll ask you to win 100 times in Battle Frontier battles.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>There are four ways to battle in the Battle Frontier:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Battle Tower<\/li>\n<li>Battle Mine<\/li>\n<li>Battle Circus<\/li>\n<li>Battle Sands<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Participating in the Battle Sands <strong>does not<\/strong> count towards the 100 wins you need, so you\u2019ll need to battle in the other three.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/040\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-battle-mine.jpg\" alt=\"The Battle Mine \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Battle Mine<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you win in the Battle Tower, Battle Mine, and\/or Battle Circus a collective 100 times, return to the Ace Trainer in the gate and she\u2019ll award you with <strong>200 BP<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1238,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1237","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1237","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1238"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1237"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1237"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}